channel.description: The latest CVEs for Jenkins Project -- Jenkins TestComplete support Plugin

item.title: CVE-2023-33002|2023-10-24T12:50:26.179Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20testcomplete%20support%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins TestComplete support Plugin 2.8.1 and earlier does not escape the TestComplete project name, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Item/Configure permission.

item.title: CVE-2023-24443|2023-10-24T12:48:34.231Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20testcomplete%20support%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins TestComplete support Plugin 2.8.1 and earlier does not configure its XML parser to prevent XML external entity (XXE) attacks.
